#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.copysign.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.copysign"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:1 of
msgid "Change the sign of x1 to that of x2, element-wise."
msgstr "将 x1 的符号更改为 x2 的符号，逐元素进行。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:3 of
msgid ""
"If both arguments are arrays or sequences, they have to be of the same "
"length. If `x2` is a scalar, its sign will be copied to all elements of "
"`x1`."
msgstr ""
"如果两个参数都是数组或序列，则它们的长度必须相同。如果 `x2` 是标量，则其"
"符号将被复制到 `x1` 的所有元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:7 of
msgid "Values to change the sign of."
msgstr "需要更改符号的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:9 of
msgid "The sign of `x2` is copied to `x1`."
msgstr "`x2` 的符号被复制到 `x1`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播输入。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign:21 of
msgid "**out** -- The values of `x1` with the sign of `x2`."
msgstr "**out** -- 具有 `x2` 符号的 `x1` 值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.copysign.copysign of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

